<section id="commands.groups.edit"><title>Edit Commands</title>
	
	<para>Standard editing commands.</para>

	<section id="command.ref.copy"><title>copy</title>
		<indexterm><primary>commands</primary><secondary>copy</secondary></indexterm>
		<para><emphasis>Syntax:</emphasis></para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para> copy ( )</para>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
		<para>Copy the current atom selection to the clipboard, ready for ((Commands: Building|#paste|pasting)).</para>
		
		<para>For example:</para>
		<synopsis>
			copy();
		</synopsis>
		
	</section>
		
